react4j.internal

Class NativeAdapterComponent<I extends Component>

  • java.lang.Object
    • react4j.internal.NativeComponent
      • react4j.internal.NativeAdapterComponent<I>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - the type of the native component.

    public abstract class NativeAdapterComponent<I extends Component>
extends NativeComponent
    This class provides a base class that designed to forward all lifecycle methods to a target component. The target component is of type Component.
